snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Sanctus Reach - Horrors of the Warp is out!
snippet.description:
Horrors of the Warp is out!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/841150/Warhammer_40000_Sanctus_Reach__Horrors_of_the_Warp/

The new expansion for Warhammer 40,000: Sactus Reach adds a new single player campaign in which Space Wolves will have to repel the tide of Chaos Daemons. Chaos Daemons themselves have been added as a new playable race in Skirmish, with loads of new units, abilities and types of weapons. It is a must-have for all Sanctus Reach fans!
